ically 9x9, 16x16, 30x16 levels. Also, there is a customizable level where you can play a huge 32x32 field with very high difficulty (guaranteed solvable)<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2671210/extras/71cf27493c53891fc625122307245d1a.poster.avif?t=1742909823\" width=616 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2671210/extras/71cf27493c53891fc625122307245d1a.webm?t=1742909823\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2671210/extras/71cf27493c53891fc625122307245d1a.mp4?t=1742909823\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2671210/extras/00520044343b767cfd2d3cd5db2db05d.webp?t=1742909823\" width=616 height=35 /></span><br>The game has a level editor! You can realize your fun and interesting ideas. The editor supports classic minesweeper and fishing mode. Levels can be shared with friends and the game community!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2671210/extras/b914d32d2812b7bd7f73c24c0392b1a1.poster.avif?t=1742909823\" width=616 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2671210/extras/b914d32d2812b7bd7f73c24c0392b1a1.webm?t=1742909823\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2671210/extras/b914d32d2812b7bd7f73c24c0392b1a1.mp4?t=1742909823\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2671210/extras/a571ea247a41bae1